data.description: Price Adjustment! Lowest priced home in Valencia Pointe! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom "Isabelle" model home with a convertible Office/Den offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, and convenience. The home features an open and spacious floor plan, with high ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space. The primary bedroom features a generous walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Valencia Point offers a wealth of amenities, including a clubhouse, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis courts, and more. Conveniently located in Boynton Beach, you will have easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major highways. Furniture may be negotiable.
